'清除段落末尾
Private Function clearParagraphEnd(str As String) As String
    clearParagraphEnd = Replace(Replace(str, Chr(10), ""), Chr(13), "")
End Function
'输入格式：附件正文前有附件或附件+数字，无冒号，且独立成段。紧邻下一行为标题行
Private Sub 附件正文()
